  X = NeOp1;
} else if (match(NeOp1, m_AllOnes())) {
  X = NeOp0;
} else {
  return nullptr;
}
```

There's no need to check for m_APInt() because m_AllOnes() already matches the all-ones constant. Let me fix this.

